NAME
    XT::Manager - manage a collection of author tests shared between multiple
    projects

SYNOPSIS
     perl-xt-manager pull --all

DESCRIPTION
    XT::Manager is a tool for sharing author test cases between multiple Perl
    projects. The command line tool `perl-xt-manager` is the primary way of
    using it.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs to
    <http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=XT-Manager>.

SEE ALSO
    XT::Manager::API, XT::Util.

